{"tid":913164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「中國正剝削我們的資源」巴基斯坦叛軍攻進中國領事館","createTime":"2018-11-23T07:51:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T08:20:58.000Z","uid":35790,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"31f57dabfe6d29c85d491a0e0b2f288bcbb86d13","tid":913164,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:51:59.000Z","msg":"「中國正剝削我們的資源」巴基斯坦叛軍攻進中國領事館<br />\n<br />\n2018-11-23 15:11<br />\n<br />\n首次上稿 15:11<br />\n更新時間 15:31<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國駐巴基斯坦南部港口城市喀拉蚩的領事館，今（23日）遭3名自殺式襲擊者攻進館內，巴國俾路支解放軍（Balochistan Liberation Army，BLA）承認犯案，因為「中國正在剝削我們的資源」。<br />\n<br />\n據《路透》報導，1位不願透露姓名的高級警官透露，2名襲擊者進入領事館的簽證處。這起攻擊造成2名警察喪命，另有1名保安受傷，巴基斯坦警方將闖入領事館內的恐怖分子包圍起來後攻堅。<br />\n<br />\nBLA在電話中告訴《路透》，這次共有3名自殺式襲擊者展開攻擊，他們衝進了中國駐喀拉蚩的領事館。據了解，中國是巴基斯坦的盟友，也是其主要的捐助者，在一帶一路的基礎設施項目中投資巴國數十億美元。<br />\n<br />\n喀拉蚩警方稍早表示，3名恐攻嫌犯都已被擊斃，外交部長庫雷希（Shah Mahmood Qureshi）則說，中國領事館的21名職員都安然無恙，已轉移到更安全的地方保護。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;"},{"pid":"e951d6a67d666fe272cbc68eb871a592a58c275b","tid":913164,"uid":35790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:53:21.000Z","msg":"一帶一路"},{"pid":"9dbd78a80f1893bcf683b4458033d480c51a561a","tid":913164,"uid":38904,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:55:40.000Z","msg":"有冇得捐錢畀班rebels<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54cc05a5aeb5263ca79efe4013c6a4b186013008","tid":913164,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:56:24.000Z","msg":"巴人未富先驕"},{"pid":"c8de4518d796c93bfe607839d874e07a45a75c30","tid":913164,"uid":163801,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:12:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n喀拉蚩警方稍早表示，3名恐攻嫌犯都已被擊斃，外交部長庫雷希（Shah Mahmood Qureshi）則說，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中國領事館的21名職員都安然無恙</strong></span>，已轉移到更安全的地方保護。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;</blockquote><br />\n點做嘢㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a05b3bda6f4df0a747353543eb92ea6aac244eb","tid":913164,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:15:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n喀拉蚩警方稍早表示，3名恐攻嫌犯都已被擊斃，外交部長庫雷希（Shah Mahmood Qureshi）則說，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中國領事館的21名職員都安然無恙</strong></span>，已轉移到更安全的地方保護。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;</blockquote><br />\n點做嘢㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望召喚佢全球兄弟，陸軍有黎！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6186c7ba7626d9e8801e642be10eb92c883c1905","tid":913164,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:16:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n喀拉蚩警方稍早表示，3名恐攻嫌犯都已被擊斃，外交部長庫雷希（Shah Mahmood Qureshi）則說，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中國領事館的21名職員都安然無恙</strong></span>，已轉移到更安全的地方保護。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;</blockquote><br />\n點做嘢㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望召喚佢全球兄弟，陸續有黎，尤其京城！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"028f9f4db57314308089eb6523880eaa2b0e14b8","tid":913164,"uid":209225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6186c7ba7626d9e8801e642be10eb92c883c1905","tid":913164,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:16:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote